snippet.title: Sea of Survivors - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Sea of Survivors is a pirate adventure bullet heaven set on the high sea. Play as the captain of a ship that can never stop moving and create a unique build with every run with an arsenal of weapon, powerful treasures and mysterious curses.

Wishlist Sea of Survivors on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2347940/Sea_of_Survivors/

Join the crew on Discord:
https://discord.gg/Zsjz7g9RrK
